						<summary>

						<p>Slab standing in survey No. 3014, south-east of the village.</p>						

						<p>Kākatīya: Pratāparudra.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1239, Pramōda,</hi> corresponding to 1317 A.D.</p>						

						<p>Badly damaged and worn out. It seems to register some gifts to god Gōpinātha. The details regarding donee are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
